room_title: Escape room "Deuces Wild" by Frisco Escape Room in Breckenridge
room_description: It’s October 20th, 1881. You are the citizens that noticed that James McWalters’ saloon wasn’t open for business on time. Concerned, you enter through the back door to find that James had been murdered by two men with knives over a poker game dispute. Can you locate both of the murder weapons to help implicate the criminals before the bad guys skip town for good?
